<template>
  Home
</template>

<script>

import {onMounted} from "vue";

export default {
  name: "Home",
  props: ['mqttClient'],
  setup(props){
    onMounted(()=>{
      props.mqttClient
          .then((client) => {
            console.log(client)
          })
          .catch((err) => {
            console.log(err)
            return null;
          });
    })
  }
}
